reviewText: Awesome season! I love it The only thing was it was missing disc 3..have no idea what episodes I missed. why was it missing a whole disc?

This is a quality police show.  Great performances by actors who later became super stars.  Several of them played many characters and roles through out the series.  Wonderful footage of the city of New York landscape and tenements.  What makes this So sad that this is the end of the series.

I love this series, sad that it went only four seasons, but the big city life filmed right there in New York was great wish they do more of that, they sure do it here in Los Angeles. I liked it so much I bought it twice.
